 	<li>Elevate Online Marketing Ltd. require a minimum of 30 days’ notice of a client’s intention to cancel a campaign.</li>
 	<li>If Elevate Online Marketing Ltd. do not receive payment we will stop working on your site optimisation until payment is received. This may negatively affect your site’s performance on the search engines and the invoiced value will still be due.</li>
 	<li>Elevate Online Marketing Ltd. may need to edit your site in order to carry out on page site optimisation work.</li>
 	<li>If the client makes changes to the website independently, it is the client’s responsibility to ensure Elevate Online Marketing Ltd. are informed of the changes. Failure to do so could result in a negative campaign performance.</li>
 	<li>Links used on a client’s behalf as part of an ongoing search engine optimisation may or may not continue to work during the term of the SEO contact or on termination.</li>
 	<li>Elevate Online Marketing Ltd. will attempt to increase the rank of your website on the Search Engines. There is however no guarantee that we can do this. Your monthly payment covers the time used to plan and execute the clients SEO campaign. Elevate Online Marketing Ltd. cannot be held responsible for Search engine algorithm changes that could negatively affect the ranking of the client’s website.</li>
 	<li>The strategies and campaign objectives created by Elevate Online Marketing Ltd. are done so on a per client basis, Elevate Online Marketing Ltd. cannot be held responsible for any negatively implied impacts of the work completed.</li>
 	<li>Elevate Online Marketing Ltd. will not disclose any back links that may be purchase as part of your SEO campaign.</li>
</ol>
<h3><strong>PPC Service</strong></h3>
<ol>
 	<li>Payments will be taken monthly for the Elevate Online Marketing Ltd. management fee starting on the day the client proceeds and every month thereafter. There will be no minimum term but Elevate Online Marketing Ltd. do require a minimum of 1 month notice of a client’s intention to cancel a campaign. Failure to provide a month’s notice will result in the next month’s invoice becoming due.</li>
 	<li>The client shall pay the chosen search engines directly for their advertising spend. Elevate Online Marketing Ltd. will manage this spend. Where a daily budget has been agreed, the client understands that Google may exceed the daily budget on one day and balance up on a different day as per their terms <a href="https://support.google.com/adwords/answer/2375423?hl=en">https://support.google.com/adwords/answer/2375423?hl=en</a></li>
 	<li>Elevate Online Marketing Ltd. can only operate on websites that are permitted to advertise on Google, further information on their policy can be found here <a href="https://support.google.com/adwordspolicy/answer/6008942">https://support.google.com/adwordspolicy/answer/6008942</a></li>
 	<li>If Elevate Online Marketing Ltd. do not receive payment, we will stop managing your PPC account until payment is received. This may negatively affect the client’s website performance and could lead to increased advertising spend.</li>
 	<li>Elevate Online Marketing Ltd. will attempt to improve your website traffic using optimised PPC. There is however no guarantee with this service. Your monthly payment covers the time used to plan and execute the clients PPC campaign.</li>
 	<li>Where conversions are measured in terms of end goals on the client site, Elevate Online Marketing Ltd. are not responsible for conversions levels in the case of changes to the site / products by the client. For instance, an increase in product price may bring the conversion rate down irrespective of any actions taken within the PPC campaign.</li>
 	<li>Elevate Online Marketing Ltd. is not associated with Google</li>
</ol>
<h3><strong>Social Media Service</strong></h3>
<ol>
 	<li>Elevate Online Marketing LTD will attempt to increase your followers / likes on Facebook / Twitter / Instagram. Your monthly payment covers the time used to plan and execute the client’s social media campaign.</li>
 	<li>If Elevate Online Marketing LTD do not receive payment we will stop managing your Social Media account until payment is received. This may negatively affect the client’s website performance and could lead to a fall in likes / followers.</li>
 	<li>The strategies and campaign objectives created by Elevate Online Marketing LTD are done so on a per client basis, Elevate Online Marketing LTD cannot be held responsible for any negatively implied impacts of the work completed.</li>
 	<li>The Elevate Online Marketing LTD Social Media service is completely separate to any other Elevate Online Marketing LTD service.</li>
 	<li>Elevate Online Marketing LTD shall make posts on behalf of the client every working day.</li>
 	<li>Elevate Online Marketing LTD require the client to create a Facebook / Twitter / Instagram account for us to carry out our services. Due to data protection, Elevate Online Marketing LTD cannot do this on behalf of the client. We will then require the client’s login details for all sites in order to carry out our Social Media campaign.</li>
 	<li>Elevate Online Marketing LTD shall provide a monthly report to the client detailing some of the achievements of the Social Media campaign. Elevate Online Marketing LTD accept no liability for any content posted that is deemed inappropriate by the client. Elevate Online Marketing LTD accept no liability for any content posted on the clients Social Media accounts by another person / user.</li>
</ol>
<h3><strong>WebCare Terms</strong></h3>
<ol>
 	<li>Elevate Online Marketing Ltd. will provide WebCare for the website if the client requires us to do so and on receipt of full payment of our hosting fees 12 months after the website went live. In doing so, Elevate Online Marketing Ltd. will provide a reliable and professional service to the client, excluding unavoidable technical failures. All hosting offered by Elevate Online Marketing Ltd. is limited to 2000mb of website space unless otherwise stated in a separate contract.</li>
 	<li>Elevate Online Marketing Ltd. offer WebCare as an annually renewable product. The date of renewal will be 12 calendar months from the date the website was made live.</li>
 	<li>Elevate Online Marketing Ltd. will contact the client 4 weeks before the renewal date, WebCare services are not obligated.</li>
 	<li>The WebCare renewal charge must be received within 10 days of the WebCare expiry date. We reserve the right to deactivate any website when the WebCare has expired, and the client has not paid the renewal charge. We reserve the right to charge an administration fee of £100 plus VAT for reactivating WebCare.</li>
 	<li>If the client does not use Elevate Online Marketing Ltd. WebCare services, then the management and hosting of the domain name are the full responsibility of the client.</li>
 	<li>If the client does not wish to renew WebCare, or do not wish to have their site hosted with us after completion, the site files and associated data can be made available to the client for free on request and the domain name can be transferred to the client’s registrar account. Should the client instruct us to upload and configure the site and domain name to a third-party server this work will be subject to charge.</li>
 	<li>Elevate Online marketing Ltd. reserve the right to delete the website from our servers 3 months after the date your WebCare service expired if you choose to not renew WebCare.</li>
 	<li>Elevate Online marketing Ltd. offer free SSL with sites we host and manage DNS for. If you wish to manage DNS independently, we cannot provide support for SSL. SSL is provided for 1 year at no charge when you purchase a website and host the website with an Elevate Online marketing Ltd. WebCare package.</li>
 	<li>SSL is provided via letsencrypt.org. If letsencrypt.org are not able to provide an SSL certificate for any reason including technical failure, Elevate Online Marketing Ltd. will make recommendations for other SSL providers. This will be charged at the advertised cost by the SSL provider as well as a £50 installation fee. The client will have the option to proceed with this SSL certificate or not.</li>
 	<li>Payments for WebCare products are non-refundable and non-transferable.</li>
 	<li>As part of all WebCare packages you receive DDoS protection. This is provided via a third party, Cloudflare Inc. Our DDoS protection is intended to provide an extra security layer to your website in the event of a DDoS attack against your website or services. If your services are interrupted or taken offline due to a DDoS attack Elevate Online marketing Ltd. will endeavour to restore these services ASAP. We cannot be held liable financially or otherwise for a DDoS attack.</li>
 	<li>Elevate Online marketing Ltd. do not take any responsibility for a client’s website rank on search engines. This also includes any potential website downtime that can occur. When updating, changing, creating and hosting a client’s website, there could be a change in the websites search engine ranking.<strong>
</strong></li>
</ol>
