"<p class="fw-bold">We’re living in a world where if you’re not on social platforms - you’re missing a trick (and living under a rock)! Social media is a place to be seen, heard and <strong><em>sell</em></strong> - it’s a piece of pie you want a big chunk of.</p>
<p>Of course not everyone has the time, know-how or creative wizardry to spend hours on Facebook or Instagram carving out a social presence.</p>
<p>ElevateOM Social Media Team at your service! No social awkwardness here, just creative minds with a hankering for brand awareness. We’ll take on those essential Social Media management tasks, maintain your online presence and power your social profiles to a higher level of awesomeness. <span class="fw-bold">Hello, new followers!</span></p>
<p><span class="fw-bold">How It Works</span><br />There’s a lot more to Social Media than “likes”. Behind the scenes it takes a lot of research and hard graft to compile, carry out and have success with a social media strategy.</p>
<p>Firstly we need to focus on your goal. Want more sales? Boost brand awareness? Increase website traffic?</p>
<p>Like many things in online marketing, it takes time to reach these goals and build an audience, and even longer to build a loyal one!</p>
<p>Our Social Media Team will apply research to your business and competitors in order to create a plan of action and social media strategy.</p>
<p>At the end of each month you’ll receive a detailed statistical report on how your social pages are performing. Great for monitoring your progress and helpful to our team for tweaking their strategy.</p>
<p>You’re probably wondering what <em>exactly</em> it is we’ll do; our SMM Team will:</p>
