 	<li>If the client does not wish to renew WebCare, the site files and associated data can be made available to the client for free on request and the domain name can be transferred to the client’s registrar account. Should the client instruct us to upload and configure the site and domain name to a third-party server this work will be subject to charge.</li>
 	<li>Elevate Online marketing LTD reserve the right to delete the website from our servers 3 months after the date your WebCare service expired if you choose to not renew WebCare.</li>
 	<li>Elevate Online marketing LTDoffer free SSL with sites we host and manage DNS for. If you wish to manage DNS independently, we cannot provide support for SSL. SSL is provided for 1 year at no charge when you purchase a website and host the website with anElevate Online marketing LTD WebCare package.</li>
 	<li>SSL is provided via letsencrypt.org. If letsencrypt.org are not able to provide an SSL certificate for any reason including technical failure,Elevate Online Marketing LTD will make recommendations for other SSL providers. This will be charged at the advertised cost by the SSL provider as well as a £50 installation fee. The client will have the option to proceed with this SSL certificate or not.</li>
 	<li>Payments for WebCare products are non-refundable and non-transferable.</li>
 	<li>As part of all WebCare packages you receive DDoS protection. This is provided via a third party, Cloudflare Inc. Our DDoS protection is intended to provide an extra security layer to your website in the event of a DDoS attack against your website or services. If your services are interrupted or taken offline due to a DDoS attack Elevate Online marketing LTD will endeavour to restore these services ASAP. We cannot be held liable financially or otherwise for a DDoS attack.</li>
 	<li>Elevate Online marketing LTDdo not take any responsibility for a client’s website rank on search engines. This also includes any potential website downtime that can occur. When updating, changing, creating and hosting a client’s website, there could be a change in the websites search engine ranking.</li>
</ol>
<h3>Domain Names and Links</h3>
<ol>
 	<li>If required, a domain name will be registered byElevate Online Marketing LTD on behalf of the client once we have received payment in full. Although the domain name is registered to Elevate Online marketing LTD, the client is the legal owner of the domain and if they request to have details changed or the domain transferred elsewhere, we will do this within a reasonable timeframe.</li>
 	<li>Elevate Online marketing LTDprovides links or references to our client’s websites solely for the convenience of prospective customers and intends that the links it provides be current and accurate but does not guarantee or warrant that such links will point to the intended client site at all times.</li>
 	<li>We place a small text link on the footer of our client’s website that simply states the website was designed byElevate Online Marketing LTD and links to our company website. This link can be removed, if required.</li>
</ol>
