<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>The most used method is certainly to offer a discount on the next purchase or booking. Both positive and negative reviews will come, but every single piece of feedback is very important to understand what your weaknesses are, and how to improve them.&nbsp;</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p><strong>Create posts and stay active on social media&nbsp;</strong></p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>Another way that can lead people to write positive reviews about your company is to stay active on social media. The people who follow the account on social media are generally interested in the products and the brand in question, so it is possible that any customer, after having had a positive experience with the company, will be inclined to leave a positive comment. The post you create has to get people to comment – why not users a question about your product?&nbsp;</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p><strong>Be present on multiple online platforms&nbsp;</strong></p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>In addition to website reviews, customers very often expect to find answers to their questions across multiple platforms, such as Google Facebook, TripAdvisor and many more.&nbsp;</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>For this reason, it is essential to be present on the main platforms used in relation to your business because you will increase your audience.&nbsp;</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

