<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>Make it easy to contact for help, information or insights on each page of your shop. Show your "community" that customer service is irreproachable and always offers a solution. Be responsive by proposing the possibility to modify the product, promotional code, free shipping, etc. Invest in customer care and communicate with customers through the various channels: web, blog, social network, newsletter.</p>
