<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>However, while it is important to inform customers, you should never overwhelm your audience either. Too much text will never be read and can completely undermine your social media strategy. Images are your best friend when it comes to generating social media engagement, and through a mixture of personalised images, trend-driven graphics, informative infographics, and relevant stories, you will find your posts get far more engagement, while still giving your audience the key facts of your brand.&nbsp;</p>
